    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'll look into why/when this broke, but `aa!(event.insightsMethod!, event.payload);` works if you assume insightsMethod isn't optional (I'm double checking why it was marked as optional, possibly for custom widgets)\r\n\r\nEDIT: it's indeed for custom widgets not sending insightsMethod, so as the default implementation it should have \r\n\r\n```ts\r\nonEvent(event, aa) {\r\nif (event.insightsMethod) {\r\n aa(event.insightsMethod, event.payload)\r\n}\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI'll update the docs",
